{"tid":2239724,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人童年好少娛樂？","createTime":"2020-10-12T07:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T17:35:08.000Z","uid":195944,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8499effb9a099dc1051b2986371fbf7082831893","tid":2239724,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個好窮 窮到屋企電視都無<br />\n<br />\n因為自悲 搞到無咩朋友<br />\n<br />\n因為呀媽迫 日日都要溫書<br />\n<br />\n好少落公園玩 好少興趣<br />\n<br />\n睇到其他人有得砌高達就好羨慕<br />\n<br />\n雖然升到上大學 （失業中<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n但童年就好似缺少咗啲野<br />\n<br />\n好想回到過去 日日落街跑跑跳跳 同其他人做朋友<br />\n<br />\n細過只識讀書 但其實小朋友嘅最重要就係要玩<br />\n<br />\n好似大人一樣有職業 小朋友嘅職業就係玩 <br />\n<br />\n後悔聽呀媽講 讀好啲書就會賺到好多錢 呃鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f779354c5bf1360d0d1f46fdfa3450f57c0f70aa","tid":2239724,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"勸告位小朋友 讀書係重要<br />\n<br />\n但識同人相處更加重要 係要親身感受 書讀唔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd5c192a118ab8ea0571716ba6c49c86929dcbb","tid":2239724,"uid":57198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"你大學讀咩"},{"pid":"0559ac4baf7c9092df97773df6a38eda404b713b","tid":2239724,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd5c192a118ab8ea0571716ba6c49c86929dcbb","tid":2239724,"uid":57198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"你大學讀咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"讀啲廢科 晒銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff08701bdf53452aeacb4947ad896cb4568bae5","tid":2239724,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"係咁架喇<br />\n香港好多垃圾家長以為死谷個條上到大學就會搵到錢<br />\n20年前可能係既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家大學生已經唔值錢 返工直程都搵唔到錢 <br />\n無樓無資產=幾叻都無用"},{"pid":"c57285b8c7c658d315483e2492cd6f4ee9437622","tid":2239724,"uid":126046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:40:06.000Z","msg":"算啦 果個年代係咁<br />\n冇咁多階級觀念 <br />\n屋村仔同有錢仔一齊讀一間學校<br />\n大家都只係想考第一 讀大學<br />\n<br />\n但係依家識人好過識字<br />\n啲人一早就入國際學校<br />\n但如果你呀媽一早領悟到依個道理<br />\n你可能連邊個係老豆都唔知"},{"pid":"79810ec8bc3ae9c1da526c6a22af07b1d9492b07","tid":2239724,"uid":297490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0559ac4baf7c9092df97773df6a38eda404b713b","tid":2239724,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd5c192a118ab8ea0571716ba6c49c86929dcbb","tid":2239724,"uid":57198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"你大學讀咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"讀啲廢科 晒銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"如果妳讀多兩年<br />\n就唔會「哂」銀紙<br />\n而係「嘥」銀紙啦"},{"pid":"d9618be3e5d3fd161a3e0dd2509d893a493a33d9","tid":2239724,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79810ec8bc3ae9c1da526c6a22af07b1d9492b07","tid":2239724,"uid":297490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0559ac4baf7c9092df97773df6a38eda404b713b","tid":2239724,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd5c192a118ab8ea0571716ba6c49c86929dcbb","tid":2239724,"uid":57198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"你大學讀咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"讀啲廢科 晒銀紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"如果妳讀多兩年<br />\n就唔會「哂」銀紙<br />\n而係「嘥」銀紙啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"讀幾多年都係浪費金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0317328671be76c68c9f8ca5ef822b0557d54a96","tid":2239724,"uid